n Wandel des politisch-medialen Altersbildes, konfrontiert diesen mit den Erzählungen älterer Menschen zu ihrem Leben im Ruhestand und überführt die Befunde in eine originelle Zeitdiagnose der alternden Gesellschaft.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aAgingxCross-cultural studies. 0aOld age pensionszGermany. 0aRetireeszGermanyvInterviews. 0aRetireeszGermanyxInterviews. 0aRetireeszGermanyxSocial conditions. 0aRetirementxSocial aspectszGermany. 4aAktivierung. 4aBevölkerung. 4aDemographie. 4aGesellschaft. 4aLebensführung. 4aNeoliberalismus. 4aOst-West-Vergleich. 4aSozialpolitik. 4aSozialstaat. 4aSoziologie. 4aSoziologische Theorie. 4aWohlfahrtsstaat. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Gerontology.2bisacsh  aNeoliberalism.  aPopulation.  aSocial Policy.  aSociety.  aSociological Theory.  aSociology.1 aLessenich, Stephan, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 avan Dyk, Silke, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2014z9783110370416oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014z9783111025223oZDB-23-TGP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript: Complete eBook-Package 2014z9783110401226oZDB-23-TGP0 cprintz978383762277540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/transcript.9783839422779?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839422779423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839422779/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL